Ing '''Dalai Lama''' ing linia o pamituki-tuki da reng mamuntukan a panrelihiun ning pamiturung [[Gelug]] (''Gelug school'') ning [[:en:Tibetan Buddhism|Tibetan Buddhism]], a yang pekapun a political ning kapamahalan a Tibetan a makabasi king [[Lhasa]] manibat kanitang kalabingpitung dilanua (''17th century'') anggang 1959. Ausan deng "[[:en:His Holiness|Ing Kayang Kabanalan]]" (''His Holiness'', HH) deng kayang talatuki, kabang deng dakal a Tibetan, palagyuan deng ''Gyalwa Rinpoche'', a mangabaldugang "Precious Victor" (Pakamalan a Migtagumpe), o ''Yishin Norbu'', meaning "Wish-fulfilling Jewel" (Iyas a Papaliari kareng Panalangin). Ing "[[Lama]]" (a mangabaldugang "[[talaturu]]" o "maestru") metung yang titulu o bansag a bibie ra kareng miayaliwang ranggu da reng paring Tibetan Buddhist.  
 
Paniwalan dang ing Dalai Lama ing [[:en:reincarnation|salukuyan a pamagkatawang tau]] ning metung a makabang pamituki-tuki da reng Tulku, o Maestrung Buddhist., a e na na darasan ning kamatayan ampong pasibayung pangabait. Pinili da reting [[:en:ascended master|maestrung minukiat na]] king sariling dang kaburian a mibait pasibayu keti ba rong dinan kamalinawan deng aliwa. Ya murin ing opisial a pekapun ning kapamahalan a Tibetan a makalual king bangsa, oCentral Tibetan Administration (CTA, ing Kalibudtang Kapanibalan a Tibetan) 

Aniang pilatan ning kalabingpitung dilanua ampo ning 1959, deng tuki-tuking Dalai Lama ing manibala king [[Kapamahalan ning Tibet]], at tatalan king maragul nang dake niti manibat king karelang tungku (cabecera o capitoliu) ning [[Lhasa]], dapot ating e pamikasundu king angganan ning karelang upayang pulitical, at ating aliwang babandi king karelang pamanalan king teritoriu. Manibat kanitang 1959, ing Dalai Lama ing mamuntukan king [[:en:Central Tibetan Administration|Kalibudtang Kapanibalan a Tibetan]] (''Central Tibetan Administration''), a makabasi king [[Dharamsala|Dharamshala]], metung a malating balen king kabitisan ning kabundukang [[Himalaya]]s king pangulung [[India]], a mituturing king sarili nang kapamahalan kilual ning bangsa (''government in exile''). Isipan dang ing Dalai Lama ing pekapun ning Pamiturung [[Gelug]] (''Gelug School''), dapot ing opisial a tatalan kaniti ya pin ing [[Ganden Tripa]], a pansamantalang pusisiun a pipilinan ning Dalai Lama (a king tutu, mas maragul a upaya). 

